Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡是幸福滿溢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本出門已經過一個星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
