Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  夫…大小…管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我大小姐就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  您今天是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來看看情況的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人過的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那麼複健治療的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們從今天開始就在這裡工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要照顧老人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連自己是誰都搞不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛伏的敵人的機關槍開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勃朗寧M嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:19.10,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,Browning M，美國槍械設計大師設計的M系槍械
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們的武器只有38
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有38式步槍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修好了  老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是親愛的從德國買回來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  戰前的布偶可是很珍貴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好愛護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來做的不錯嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小孩子是可以跨越年齡障礙的  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是他們都經常把自己關在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且一直到深夜都還亮著燈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可能是因為有著很多煩惱而睡不著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是正值複雜難懂的年紀的男孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過更為擔心的是  黑色幽靈會再來找他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以大意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點睏  先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那我要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末摘小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟我說的是什麼事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話  說來聽聽吧  大端先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是個好人啊  末摘小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且做事熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在最後我想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於老夫能力的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力？  大端先生你應該是普通人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢查的時候也沒發現超能力的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很少見的能力  所以很難被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一種合成能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰的惡作劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.00,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,規則1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.00,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,寫在這本筆記上的事情有很高的幾率變為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.00,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只限於有可能會發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Serendipity？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以帶來幸運的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有這樣的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我需要媒介才能夠使用這個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓能力寄宿的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這本筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去不過是非常普通的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要把它緊貼在我身上數個月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且一刻不停地灌輸念力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本筆記本…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:06:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能成為操控所有機率的   令人聞風喪膽的「如願以償筆記」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段期間你不洗澡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不洗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是很髒嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫在這本筆記上的事情有很高的幾率變為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只限於有可能會發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得這本筆記有點臭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繃帶和藥膏…  該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生  你這姿勢是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有比這更讓人在意的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用方法寫的非常詳細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用透視也只能看到這些規則
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這絕對是別人的東西不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都看不到不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫上內容時腦中浮現的景象越鮮明  實現的幾率就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連LV7都無法透視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午3點16分  賢木修二在朋友的公寓裡因為心臟衰竭而....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說了這可能是真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為腦中的景象很鮮明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕  妳實在是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼像這種的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生馬上打開客廳的門進入這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訓練怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞不清楚  說是預定變更了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  一臉像看到幽靈的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什麼願望都能實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法筆記本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送給別人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大概是在一個月之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  打擾您休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們發現了您的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您能將那罕見的能力借給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我打算送給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連續10次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz334.4\pos(893,454)}骰子連續出現1點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不會錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本筆記能夠操控機率  改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是超能力的一種嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠隨心所欲地操控未來  那確實是最強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是有人想對那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不太合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接寫在筆記上不是更直接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為LV太低而起不了那麼大的作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能期待太大的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須從小事一點一點地累積
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小氣的規則啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大小的標準是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我測試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木修二得到巨大的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真這麼寫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人都會這樣寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在皆本的公寓撿到這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我掉的一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生也好小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提  我們也試著寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}常盤奈津子  和貝克漢姆約會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}野分螢  挖出石油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該把管理官叫來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的話  也沒那麼緊要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我再調查看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  皆本君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  {\i1}Children{\i} 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在待機室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是有功課要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近都很忙  沒怎麼睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那麼有什麼新發現就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.82,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,規則4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.82,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,從筆記上撕下的頁面也是能夠使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些從筆記上偷偷地撕下來的頁面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管寫什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能一個人獨佔皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為皆本先生只有一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果我們都這麼寫的話  會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:06.05,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,規則5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果寫下了無法同時成立的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼新寫的內容優先實現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3個人之中只有一個人寫的會實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們已經約好了  誰都不會寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會寫的  這兩個傢伙肯定會寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是真槍實彈的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何我都要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  妳們不寫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在找機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用念力打倒她們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  這樣馬上就會穿幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後寫的內容優先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能讓她們知道我什麼時候寫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是謀略戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看來  必須嚴加警戒的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣的發展嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是妳們犯了致命的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我想不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太笨了  所以想不出什麼特別的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先寫增加零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}零用錢增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希望葵和紫穗永遠幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真替自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就寫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}讓胸部變大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希望薰和紫穗能遇到很多好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要寫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希望自己的心靈更加純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希望小薰和小葵永遠是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是摯友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始寫作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  待會借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先吃點零食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們倆都小看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才寫的不過是普通的紙片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在把筆記本上的紙片發給三人的時候確實都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只把自己的偷偷換成假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是巧妙的作戰方案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵和紫穗突然睡意襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來的時候忘記了筆記本的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大端先生您有這份心意  我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我要去準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實這個世上還有一本  「如願以償筆記」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡CHIRUCHIRU哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,チルチルは僕も好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如願以償記事本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}How to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}<規則1>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}這本筆記上所述之事\N有高幾率成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}但只限可能發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}<規則2>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}寫入時腦中浮現的\N景象越鮮明\N  實現的幾率就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}<規則3>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}不要太過期待\N實現大的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}從小事開始累積
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}<規則4>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}筆記中取下的碎片\N也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}<規則5>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.30,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}所述願望產生矛盾\N之時 以後載者為准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會念不會寫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,読めるけど書けない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還…還有一本嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埋在那棵樹下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分析已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去了一下廁所而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著筆記本去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本是不會做這種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把筆記本放下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會這麼認為？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能沒發現筆記本被撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你卻不在意{\i1}Children{\i} 的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你不是皆本  那麼就是有能力冒充他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這種超能力者是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然筆記的影響力並不大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡意突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  至少能夠幫助我進入B.A.B.E.L
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這本筆記沒有把皆本那麼快叫回來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.55,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木修二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.55,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太過疲勞而昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止都在我的計畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又熱又潮濕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我忍受不了老年人的體臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭的是筆記本！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們太差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧我還當妳們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話原封不動還給妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們全都睡了快一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過筆記本似乎沒有消除記憶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之不准偷跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去房裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  只有醫生在啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法讀取這1～2小時內的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆記本也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼應該是在局長或者奶奶那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁她們倆還沒有發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在用瞬移…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在想什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的約定呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  睡相真難看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太粗俗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人都活了幾十年了還跟小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有資格說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就把B.A.B.E.L的所有系統都改寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的資料也換成假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們再也無法偵測到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是這次的目的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便還發現了限制器解除用手機的備用品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算妳再神通廣大  也無法阻止我入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我做好隨時被襲擊的覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在把B.A.B.E.L滅掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢  我現在想好好玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始裁決了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生強烈愛上{\i1}The Children{\i} 的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管誰被選上  其他人都不准有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡我們之中的誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們在說什麼傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂姆和巴雷特失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好是黑色幽靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是洗腦沒有完全解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼必須要快點去救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  {\i1}Children{\i} 出動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Children{\i} 解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誠心許願的話就一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強烈的心意能改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋  藏哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還和黑色幽靈有所牽連嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大端先生說的  能夠實現願望改變未來的筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老爺爺可能是信口開河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是信口開河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有願望的話  就寫在這上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}取回記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}恢復失去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是想取回記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己的名字都不知道   實在無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是失去的記憶恢復的話  肯定會更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要和他一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾出去  怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱隱約約地知道過去的回憶都是些痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了一切的我沒有想要實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說沒有任何願望這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  那麼這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希望兩人能夠交到好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  不壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你好久了  這個是蒂姆你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是虎MATE的限定CHIRUCHIRU掛鏈手辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實不瞞你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是絕對CHIRUCHIRU的公認網站的管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你是「CHIRUCHIRU是我的老婆」先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是昨天一起做實況的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你是…「CHIRUCHIRU好可愛啊CHIRUCHIRU」君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈友人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們半夜不睡原來是因為這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺異常地興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興致好高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看上去非常意氣相投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟筆記本上寫的一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是筆記的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼許願的人不是妳們自己嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓超能力者…讓他人獲得幸福可能就是妳們的超能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了  皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒回答要選擇我們之中的誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆一點回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們說什麼傻話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對妳們三人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准用這招！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候認真回答是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話  我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會寂寞地跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點長大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候我會給答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的在等待那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是為此才活到現在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺和平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這個皆本先生好讚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是萌？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在萌嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它什麼公平競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我寫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  我願意為此去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在騙我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著  聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在玩些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情處理完了就早點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老頭居然寫了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.72,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,拿走筆記的人在有效期限內盡情玩樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效日期是到今天吧  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心了  那兩個人能變得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我有點擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然先把大端先生埋的筆記挖出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  我本來就打算給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼妳已經寫好願望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  已經寫了3個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  希望明天也是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  希望洗好的衣物能快點乾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是  能做出好吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太貪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的願望確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,細微地實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微早點回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然搞錯而去參加了精銳部隊的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這副模樣回來也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i} 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  三位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜升上五年級
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又長大一點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵部少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有地方和平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有地方是什麼地方啊  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論如何都想和妳們一起慶祝妳們的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會陪我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:24:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第47話  「一場春夢！明日的回憶」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本…那傢伙來了之後一切都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  這樣下去妳會…
Dialogue: 5,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐  所以不會輸！
